Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.62,0:00:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight. We're gonna be late\Nfor the Nightmare Night Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.38,0:00:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.53,0:00:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...that one creaky grandpa\Nfrom Ponyville Retirement Village?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Star Swirl the Bearded.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.34,0:00:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Father of the omnimorphic spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.91,0:00:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you even read that book I gave you\Nabout obscure unicorn history?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.52,0:00:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds important!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.33,0:00:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nightmare Night! What a fright!\NGive us something sweet to bite!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, everypony. Great costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.41,0:00:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy Nightmare Night, Granny Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.21,0:00:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have been\Nasleep five hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Pipsqueak the Pirate, at your service.\NIt's my very first Nightmare Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.11,0:01:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you moved here from Trottingham?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.99,0:01:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No. My very first Nightmare Night ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough chitchat! Time is candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.56,0:01:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, aren't you\Na little old for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Too old for free candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.61,0:01:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.24,0:01:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.42,0:01:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Great costume, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you make a fantastic weirdo clown.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.31,0:01:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A clown?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.89,0:01:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the borders on these robes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,These are hoof-stitched!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.03,0:01:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Star Swirl the Bearded is only the most\Nimportant conjurer of the pre-classical era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He created more than two hundred spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He even has a shelf in the Canterlot\Nlibrary of magic named after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should start up a pony group\Nto teach ponies of our history.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.67,0:02:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet everypony would love it.\NDon't you, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look. We're here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we get something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight! Twilight! Look at our haul!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we went to Cheerilee's house\Nand we got a bunch more goodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-Didn't we, Pip?\N-Sure did!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we had to stop and wait\Nfor Granny Smith and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash! That wasn't very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lighten up, old-timer. This is\Nthe best night of the year for pranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Look what you did to Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, it's all in good fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Oh! There's another group over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy Nightmare Night, Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.98,0:03:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Howdy, Spike. Hey, Twilight.\NNice costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! I'm a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She means me, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,With that beard, I reckon you're\Nsome sorta country music singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,While y'all are here, you feel like\Nbobbin' for an apple?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And welcome to\Nthe Nightmare Night Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, all the little ponies, who\Nhave been out collecting sweets...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...should follow our friend Zecora\Nto hear the legend of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nightmare Moooon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Spooky voice might work better\Nif she wasn't dressed like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me and very soon\NYou'll hear the tale of Nightmare Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen close, my little dears.\NI'll tell you where you got your fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Of Nightmare Night, so dark and scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.99,0:04:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Of Nightmare Moon, who makes you wary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Every year we put on a disguise\NTo save ourselves from her searching eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Nightmare Moon wants just one thing:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.76,0:05:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,To gobble up ponies in one quick swing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hungrily she soars the sky.\NIf she sees nopony, she passes by.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So if she comes and all is clear,\NEquestria is safe another year!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Miss Zecora.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If we wear costumes to hide\Nfrom Nightmare Moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.47,0:05:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...so she won't gobble us up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...how come we still need to\Ngive her some of our candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A perfect question, my little friend!\NFor Nightmare Moon you must not offend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.71,0:05:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Fill up her belly with a treat or two...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So she won't return to come eat YOUUU!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony! Just dump some\Ncandy and get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,IT'S NIGHTMARE MOON! RUUUN!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,CITIZENS OF PONYVILLE!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,WE HAVE GRACED YOUR TINY\NVILLAGE WITH OUR PRESENCE...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...SO THAT YOU MIGHT BEHOLD\NTHE REAL PRINCESS OF THE NIGHT!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A CREATURE OF NIGHTMARE IS\NNO LONGER, BUT INSTEAD...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...A PONY WHO DESIRES\NYOUR LOVE AND ADMIRATION.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,TOGETHER WE SHALL CHANGE\NTHIS DREADFUL CELEBRATION...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...INTO A BRIGHT AND\NGLORIOUS FEEEAST!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that, everypony?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nightmare Moon says\Nshe's gonna feast on us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, children, no! You no longer\Nhave reason to fear us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Screams of delight is\Nwhat your princess desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:08:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Not screams of terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.78,0:08:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thy princess of the night hath arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well then! Be that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't even bother with\Nthe traditional royal farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't talk to her!\NShe's Nightmare Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the Elements of Harmony\Nchange her back to good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems like she's having\Nsome trouble adjusting...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...after being gone\Nfor a thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Star Swirl the Bearded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Commendable costume.\NThou even got the bells right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, finally! Somepony\Nwho gets my costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I just came to welcome you\Nto our celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My actual name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight Sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,IT WAS THOU WHO UNLEASHED\NTHE POWERS OF HARMONY UPON US...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.89,0:09:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...AND TOOK AWAY OUR DARK POWERS!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was a good thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course! We\Ncould not be happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that not clear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you kind of sound\Nlike you're yelling at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the traditional\Nroyal Canterlot voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It is tradition to speak\Nusing the royal "we"...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...and to use THIS MUCH VOLUME\NWHEN ADDRESSING OUR SUBJECTS!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that might explain why\Nyour appearance was met with...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...mixed results.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I think if you just changed\Nyour approach a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...you might be met\Nwith a warmer reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,CHANGE OUR APPROACH?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Or the volume.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. We have been locked away\Nfor a thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We are... not sure we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, princess. Fluttershy\Ncan give you some great pointers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She's delicate and demure\Nwith the sweetest little voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,GO AWAY! NO CANDY HERE! VISITORS\NNOT WELCOME ON NIGHTMARE NIGHT!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.85,0:10:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, it's me, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, and Nightmare Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nightmare Moon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy... you remember Princess Luna?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.81,0:10:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,CHARMED!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,TWILIGHT SPARKLE HATH SPOKEN\NOF THE SWEETNESS OF THY VOICE.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,WE ASK, THOU TEACHEST TO US\NTO SPEAK AS THOU SPEAKEST!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,SHALL OUR LESSONS BEGIN?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,SHALL WE MIMIC THY VOICE?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,HOW IS THIS?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:10:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect. Lesson over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A little quieter, princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,HOW IS... this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Better. Right, Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.61,0:11:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How... about... now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're getting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And... how about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,AH, THANK YOU, DEAR FLUTTERSHY!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,OUR NORMAL SPEAKING\NVOICE SHALL SURELY...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...WIN US THE HEARTS\NOF THY FELLOW VILLAGERS.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy! You've gotta hide us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nightmare Moon is here and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She stole Fluttershy's voice so she\Ncan't scream when she GOBBLES HER UP!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,NAY, CHILDREN, WAIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... nay, children, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, princess. Time for plan B.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It is of no use, Twilight Sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They have never liked us\Nand they never shall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend Applejack is one of the\Nmost likeable ponies around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll have some ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Heee...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.93,0:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoop. Careful there, partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.99,0:12:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The princess is looking for a little\Nadvice on how to fit in around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"Fit in"? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... that's easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All you gotta do is have\Nthe right attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Loosen up a bit, be positive,\Nplay a few games, have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this "fun" thou speakest of?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.33,0:12:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Pray tell, what purpose do these serve?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to land the\Nsp-sp-spiders on the web.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it, princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Your princess enjoys this... fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In what other ways\Nmay we experience it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire away, princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha! The fun has been doubled!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try bobbin' for apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We got the best apples\Nin Equestria here, princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask that thou call us... me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...Luna, fair Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear me, villagers!\NAll of you! Call me Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me to this bobbing apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoooa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, gals. Anypony seen Pip?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost him the last time\Nwe had to run...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,NIGHTMARE MOON IS\NGOBBLING PIPSQUEAK!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,EVERYPONY RUUUN!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Heeelp! My backside has been gobbled!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,'Tis a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:14:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thy backside is whole and ungobbled,\Nthou ungrateful whelp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fair villagers, please do not back away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us join together in...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not enough fun for you?\NWhat say you to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huzzah! How many points do I receive?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,As your princess we command you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.73,0:14:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,BE STILL!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess, remember! Watch the screaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,NO, TWILIGHT SPARKLE!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,WE MUST USE THE TRADITIONAL\NROYAL CANTERLOT VOICE...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...FOR WHAT WE ARE ABOUT TO SAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,SINCE YOU CHOOSE TO FEAR YOUR PRINCESS\NRATHER THAN LOVE HER...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...AND DISHONOR HER WITH THIS\NINSULTING CELEBRATION...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...WE DECREE THAT NIGHTMARE\NNIGHT SHALL BE CANCELED!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,FOREVER!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot. We had everything goin' our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna was happy, everypony in town\Nwas happy. Now look at 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wanted to be a zombie next year!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do what I do best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lecture her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me be, Twilight Sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess. I'm sorry it hasn't\Nworked out how we wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have to believe me when\NI tell you that Nightmare Night...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...is one of the most popular\Ncelebrations we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,By all the adoring shrieks\Nof the children as they run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No shrieking. No squealing\Nor screaming either. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.06,0:16:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I want you to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And I promise that it's safe, but you\Nreally, really, really can't shriek.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you promise not to shriek?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, you remember\NPrincess Luna, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. The ringleader of the\Nfrightened children.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hast thou come to make peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nightmare Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.29,0:17:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.07,0:17:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She's changed, Pinkie!\NShe's not evil or scary anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And she definitely doesn't\Nwant to gobble you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, duh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that. Sheesh, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm almost as big as her.\NHow's she gonna gobble me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So why do you keep\Nrunning away and screaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.50,0:18:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it's just\Nreally fun to be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, you're a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not. I'm a chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna!\NI've finally figured out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...why you're having\Nso much trouble being liked!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me if I withhold my enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.75,0:18:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me. I'll explain\Neverything on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh. I never thought my\Nvery first Nightmare Night...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...would be my very last.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, little Pip. Now don't you fret.\NNightmare Night's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have candy left to give,\NSo Nightmare Moon might let us live.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Come on, little ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's Nightmare Night without\Nthe annual candy offering?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want Nightmare Moon\Nto gobble you up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...dooo youuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, the rainbow wig just kills it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, kids!\NDoesn't that sound like fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Nightmare Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.49,0:19:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,CITIZENS OF PONYVILLE!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU WERE WISE TO BRING THIS CANDY TO ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I AM PLEASED WITH YOUR OFFERING.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,SO PLEASED THAT I MAY JUST EAT IT...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...INSTEAD OF EATING YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not certain that did what\Nyou meant for it to do, Twilight Sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,For what? For... for them\Nto scream some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Princess Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I know there's not gonna be\Nany more Nightmare Night...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...but do you suppose maybe\Nyou could come back next year...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...and scare us again anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Child. Are thou saying that thou...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...likest me to scare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really fun! Scary, but fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It... is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Nightmare Night is my\Nfavorite night of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then. We shall have to bring...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.43,0:20:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...NIGHTMARE NIGHT BACK!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.54,0:20:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my favorite princess ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She said yes, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,YAY!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,See? They really do like you, princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it be true?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,OH, MOST WONDERFUL OF...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, most wonderful of nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dear Princess Celestia."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"When you first sent me to Ponyville,\NI didn't know anything about friendship."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"I met somepony tonight who\Nwas having the same problem..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"...your sister, Princess Luna."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"She taught me that one of the best\Nthings you can do with friendship..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"...is to give it to others and\Nhelp them find it themselves."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.86,0:20:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"And I'm happy to report that\Nall of Ponyville has learned..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:21:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"...that even if somepony seems\Na little intimidating, even scary..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"...when you offer them your friendship,\Nyou'll discover a whole new pony underneath."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"And even if my Star Swirl the Bearded\Ncostume didn't go over..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"...this still turned out to be\Nthe best Nightmare Night ever."
